The base package of the common plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver.

Class Summary
AbstractModelTransformer<T> A convenience abstract class to be extended by clients that transform a model and need a console and a URI.
Av2BaseEqualityHelper A class for determining whether advice elements are equivalent to base elements.
GeKoBridge A utility class containing methods that are used by multiple GeKo plug-ins and that are GeKo specific (so they do not belong to an adapter class of lu.uni.geko.util.bridges).

(Note that it is disputable whether this class conforms to the bridge pattern as we are currently only providing one implementation and the "abstractions" can be regarded as low-level.)
GeKoConstants A utility class containing all the constants needed by individual GeKo plug-ins.
GeKoVariables Deprecated.
HashMappedJoinPoint An implementation of the convenience representation (or proxy) of a JoinPoint using a HashMap for the mapping from pointcut elements to matched base elements.
MainFeatureIgnorer A utility class to access the functionality provided by extensions of the FeatureIgnorerExt extension point.
 

Package lu.uni.geko.common Description

The base package of the common plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. It contains GeKo-specific concepts that are used by multiple GeKo plug-ins.
